WEBVTT FILE

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Universities and school districts are collecting more data than ever before. This data is priceless.

2
00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:12.000
The big question is, do we make the best usage of big data in education?

3
00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:21.500
Big data is a key to understanding how students are learning. Data-driven education relies on academic assessment as an integral part of continuous development.

4
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:37.000
Whether you report your assessment findings for internal or accreditation purposes, there has been a common problem with data scattered between different sources.
Scattered data makes it very time consuming, and in some cases impossible to analyze and visualize.

5
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:47.000
This problem puts a burden on teachers and administrators to make the best use of their data.
In some cases, it prevents institutions from seeing the big picture.

6
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.000
Introducing EdVeu’s reporting tool.

7
00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:56.500
A tool that offers	a solution to make big assessment data more accessible to stakeholders.

8
00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:10.000
EdVeu’s reporting tool streamlines the assessment process through LMS integration. Integrating
with your learning management system, the reporting tool helps your institution keep data centralized in one location.





